dc_title_s: Land Use Eau Claire County, WI 2019
dc_description_s: This data represents land use for Eau Claire County, Wisconsin in 2019. [Geodatabase feature class representing future land use polygons in Eau Claire County, WI. The data is developed in conjunction with comprehensive planning efforts and is used in decision making regarding rezoning, new development, etc.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
